{"title":"记一次url传参引发的bug","uid":"ed6fe211e2d128757db0d79a4c616ca7","slug":"记一次url传参引发的bug","date":"2021-12-24T18:31:43.000Z","updated":"2023-04-14T14:16:33.245Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/记一次url传参引发的bug.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"bug-复现\"><a href=\"#bug-复现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"bug 复现\"></a>bug 复现</h2><p>小程序开发的时候我们之前需要跳转第三方的 webview 页面，一般传参数的时候</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">Taro.navigateTo(&#123;\n  url: &#96;&#x2F;pages&#x2F;webview&#x2F;index?url&#x3D;url&#96;,\n&#125;)</code></pre>\n\n<p>这个时候我们在 webview 页面获取 url 的参数</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const url &#x3D; Taro.getCurrentInstance().router?.params?.url || &#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<p>url 后面没有添加参数，获取的时候也是没什么问题，但是 url 后面有参数，<br>诸如<a href=\"https://bot.biyouxinli.com/lianxin-botserver/openApi/gotoPsyBot?channel=TXHBOT&chnlCode=8BFE42DF24C45563B5EA6E82C67AF8139EC3757CFF1FC3E322D5CE2F41F97C407B021F83A6EF1ED3DD65CEE6&unionId=\">https://bot.biyouxinli.com/lianxin-botserver/openApi/gotoPsyBot?channel=TXHBOT&amp;chnlCode=8BFE42DF24C45563B5EA6E82C67AF8139EC3757CFF1FC3E322D5CE2F41F97C407B021F83A6EF1ED3DD65CEE6&amp;unionId=</a><br>我们再像上面的方式获取 url，就会出现错误，拿不到原始完整的 url</p>\n<h2 id=\"encodeURI-encodeURIComponent-有什么区别\"><a href=\"#encodeURI-encodeURIComponent-有什么区别\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"encodeURI,encodeURIComponent 有什么区别?\"></a>encodeURI,encodeURIComponent 有什么区别?</h2><p>它们都是编码 URL，唯一区别就是编码的字符范围，其中</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>encodeURI 方法不会对下列字符编码 ASCII 字母 数字 ~!@#$&amp;<em>()&#x3D;:&#x2F;,;?+’<br>encodeURIComponent 方法不会对下列字符编码 ASCII 字母 数字 ~!</em>()’</p></blockquote>\n<p>所以 encodeURIComponent 比 encodeURI 编码的范围更大。</p>\n<p>实际例子来说，encodeURIComponent 会把 http:&#x2F;&#x2F; 编码成 http%3A%2F%2F 而 encodeURI 却不会。</p>\n<h2 id=\"webview-传参-URL-正确的方式\"><a href=\"#webview-传参-URL-正确的方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"webview 传参 URL 正确的方式\"></a>webview 传参 URL 正确的方式</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; 编码\nTaro.navigateTo(&#123;\n  url: &#96;&#x2F;pages&#x2F;webview&#x2F;index?url&#x3D;$&#123;encodeURIComponent(live)&#125;&#96;,\n&#125;)\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 解码\nconst url &#x3D; decodeURIComponent(\n  Taro.getCurrentInstance().router?.params?.url || &#39;&#39;\n)</code></pre>\n","feature":false,"text":"bug 复现小程序开发的时候我们之前需要跳转第三方的 webview 页面，一般传参数的时候 Taro.navigateTo(&#123; url: &#96;&#x2F;pages&#x2F;webview&#x2F;index?url&#x3D;url&#96;, &#125...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Note","slug":"Note","count":6,"path":"api/categories/Note.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Bug","slug":"Bug","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Bug.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#bug-%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">bug 复现</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#encodeURI-encodeURIComponent-%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">encodeURI,encodeURIComponent 有什么区别?</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#webview-%E4%BC%A0%E5%8F%82-URL-%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">webview 传参 URL 正确的方式</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"hyzhao","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"A blog recording my life","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Position:fixed 一定是相对于浏览器窗口进行定位吗?","uid":"0fc4b7b62a60308f2908e30d24faee42","slug":"position:fixed 一定是相对于浏览器窗口进行定位吗?","date":"2022-01-11T18:37:28.000Z","updated":"2023-04-14T14:16:33.245Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/position:fixed 一定是相对于浏览器窗口进行定位吗?.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"前言position:fixed 前面一直以为是浏览器窗口进行定位；最近工作中出现一个 bug，将弹框组件（弹框是 fixed 定位）写下 tabcont 中，页面显示弹框是相对于 tabcont 进行定位。这个 bug 出现直接颠覆自己认知； 重新认识一下MDN Web Doc...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[